transcript.text: [Music] all right you made it all the way to the end of practical application data modeling we hope that you enjoyed it and that you learned a lot check out some of our other courses if you haven't yet datastock's enterprise operations with apache cassandra is a great introduction on the care and feeding of your apache cassandra clusters when you're feeling up to the challenge you can also check out the datastax 300 level courses to deep dive into dse analytics with apache spark dse search or dse graph also make sure you check out the distributed data show and our success segments on data stacks academy these short webcasts and videos jump into all sorts of cool and interesting topics
